  <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body>
<div class="center-jumbotron">

<div class="box text-center">
 <h3 class="text-uppercase"><%= t('.s_title') %></h3>
 <h4 class="text-muted"><span class="accent"><%=t('.p_text0')%></span></h4><%= t('.p_text') %></p><br />
 </div>
<!-- service carousel -->
  <style>
  .carousel-inner > .carousel-item > img,
  .carousel-inner > .carousel-item > a > img {
        width: 35%;
      height: 50%;

      margin: auto;
  }
  </style>

  <div id="carousel2" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
  <!-- Indicators -->
  <ul class="carousel-indicators">
    <li data-target="#carousel2" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
    <li data-target="#carousel2" data-slide-to="1"></li>
    <li data-target="#carousel2" data-slide-to="2"></li>
  </ul>

  <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <img src="<%= asset_path 'service1.JPG' %>" alt="3dmodel">
      <div class="carousel-caption">
        <h3><%= t('.carousel1') %></h3>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img src="<%= asset_path 'service2.JPG' %>" alt="drawing">
      <div class="carousel-caption">
        <h3><%= t('.carousel2') %></h3>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img src="<%= asset_path 'service3.JPG' %>" alt="visualization">
      <div class="carousel-caption">
        <h3><%= t('.carousel3') %></h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
    
  <!-- Left and right controls -->
  <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carousel2" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
  </a>
  <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carousel2" data-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
  </a>
</div>
<script>
$(document).ready(function(){
    // Activate Carousel
    $("#carousel2").carousel();
    
    // Enable Carousel Indicators
    $(".item1").click(function(){
        $("#carousel2").carousel(0);
    });
    $(".item2").click(function(){
        $("#carousel2").carousel(1);
    });
    $(".item3").click(function(){
        $("#carousel2").carousel(2);
    });

    
    // Enable Carousel Controls
    $(".left").click(function(){
        $("#carousel2").carousel("prev");
    });
    $(".right").click(function(){
        $("#carousel2").carousel("next");
    });
});
</script>

<p><%= t('.support') %></p>
</div>
<section id="faq">
  <div class="lead">
    <h1> FAQ </h1>
    <p><strong>How to order?</strong></p>
    <p>A: The best way is to fullfill the cart with items and complete an order, if you found suitable items on site, and that is the way your order will be completed. You will receive its confirmation and sum on mail you submitted. This doesn't lead to payment processing, its still just an inquiry for production.</p>
    <p><strong>What if I want something different from what I see on the site? </strong></p>
    <p>A: Complete the inquiry form for us to develop and supply a custom order.</p>
  </div>
</section>
</body>
</html>